headline: Landstar Enhances Its Board of Directors, Appoints Barr Blanton and Melanie Housey Hart
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Oct. 30, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Landstar System, Inc. (NASDAQ: LSTR), a technology-enabled, asset-light provider of integrated freight transportation solutions, delivering safe, specialized transportation services, announced today the addition of Barr Blanton and Melanie Housey Hart to its Board of Directors. headline: 5 Must-Read Analyst Questions From Pool’s Q3 Earnings Call
